    "Similar findings were mentioned from a prior study that examined how people leveraged Replika, another AI-powered customizable agent, to cope with their grief related to deceased loved ones [101].",
    "This observation highlighted participants' needs for multifaceted support, similarly shown in prior studies, where peer support groups, family support, and professional counseling are often used in combination [30,36,61].",
    "Besides, in the face of frustrations, participants delved into deeper and more complex emotional experiences.",
    "During the study, some participants made the chatbot mirror themselves, seeking a way to speak to their inner thoughts from an objective bystander view.",
